{"id":175,"ayahs":[{"number":188,"arabic":"قُل لَّآ أَمْلِكُ لِنَفْسِى نَفْعًۭا وَلَا ضَرًّا إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ ۚ وَلَوْ كُنتُ أَعْلَمُ ٱلْغَيْبَ لَٱسْتَكْثَرْتُ مِنَ ٱلْخَيْرِ وَمَا مَسَّنِىَ ٱلسُّوٓءُ ۚ إِنْ أَنَا۠ إِلَّا نَذِيرٌۭ وَبَشِيرٌۭ لِّقَوْمٍۢ يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"Say [O Prophet]: \"It is not within my power to bring benefit to, or avert harm from, myself, except as God may please. And if I knew that which is beyond the reach of human perception, abundant good fortune-would surely have fallen to my lot, and no evil would ever have touched me. I am nothing but a warner, and a herald of glad tidings unto people who will believe.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1142.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":84475,"position":1,"arabic":"قُل","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84476,"position":2,"arabic":"لَّآ","translation":"\"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84477,"position":3,"arabic":"أَمْلِكُ","translation":"\"ক্ষমতা রাখি আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84478,"position":4,"arabic":"لِنَفْسِى","translation":"জন্যে আমার নিজের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84479,"position":5,"arabic":"نَفْعًۭا","translation":"কোনো লাভের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84480,"position":6,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84481,"position":7,"arabic":"ضَرًّا","translation":"কোনো ক্ষতির","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84482,"position":8,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84483,"position":9,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84484,"position":10,"arabic":"شَآءَ","translation":"ইচ্ছে করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84485,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84487,"position":12,"arabic":"وَلَوْ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84488,"position":13,"arabic":"كُنتُ","translation":"আমি ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84489,"position":14,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","translation":"আমি জানি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84490,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْبَ","translation":"অদৃশ্যকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84491,"position":16,"arabic":"لَٱسْتَكْثَرْتُ","translation":"অবশ্যই আমি অনেক নিতাম","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84492,"position":17,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84493,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْخَيْرِ","translation":"কল্যাণ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84494,"position":19,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84495,"position":20,"arabic":"مَسَّنِىَ","translation":"আমাকে স্পর্শ করতো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84496,"position":21,"arabic":"ٱلسُّوٓءُ ۚ","translation":"কোনো অকল্যাণ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84498,"position":22,"arabic":"إِنْ","translation":"(প্রকৃতপক্ষে) নই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84499,"position":23,"arabic":"أَنَا۠","translation":"আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84500,"position":24,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84501,"position":25,"arabic":"نَذِيرٌۭ","translation":"একজন সতর্ককারী","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84502,"position":26,"arabic":"وَبَشِيرٌۭ","translation":"ও সুসংবাদদাতা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84503,"position":27,"arabic":"لِّقَوْمٍۢ","translation":"জন্যে ঐ সম্প্রদায়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84504,"position":28,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"(যারা) ঈমান আনে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_188_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84505,"position":29,"arabic":"١٨٨","translation":"(১৮৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":189,"arabic":"۞ هُوَ ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكُم مِّن نَّفْسٍۢ وَٰحِدَةٍۢ وَجَعَلَ مِنْهَا زَوْجَهَا لِيَسْكُنَ إِلَيْهَا ۖ فَلَمَّا تَغَشَّىٰهَا حَمَلَتْ حَمْلًا خَفِيفًۭا فَمَرَّتْ بِهِۦ ۖ فَلَمَّآ أَثْقَلَت دَّعَوَا ٱللَّهَ رَبَّهُمَا لَئِنْ ءَاتَيْتَنَا صَٰلِحًۭا لَّنَكُونَنَّ مِنَ ٱلشَّٰكِرِينَ","translation":"IT IS HE who has created you [all] out of one living entity, and out of it brought into being its mate, so that man might incline [with love] towards woman. And so, when he has embraced her, she conceives [what at first is] a light burden, and continues to bear it. Then, when she grows heavy [with child], they both call unto God, their Sustainer, \"If Thou indeed grant us a sound [child], we shall most certainly be among the grateful!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1143.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":84551,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ هُوَ","translation":"(আল্লাহ) তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84552,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84553,"position":3,"arabic":"خَلَقَكُم","translation":"সৃষ্টি করেছেন তোমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84554,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84555,"position":5,"arabic":"نَّفْسٍۢ","translation":"ব্যক্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84556,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةٍۢ","translation":"একই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84557,"position":7,"arabic":"وَجَعَلَ","translation":"এবং বানিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84558,"position":8,"arabic":"مِنْهَا","translation":"হতে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84559,"position":9,"arabic":"زَوْجَهَا","translation":"জোড়া তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84560,"position":10,"arabic":"لِيَسْكُنَ","translation":"যেন সে শান্তি পায়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84561,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَيْهَا ۖ","translation":"কাছে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84563,"position":12,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর  যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84564,"position":13,"arabic":"تَغَشَّىٰهَا","translation":"সে তাকে ঢেকে নেয় (সংগত হয়)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84565,"position":14,"arabic":"حَمَلَتْ","translation":"(স্ত্রী) গর্ভধারণ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84566,"position":15,"arabic":"حَمْلًا","translation":"গর্ভ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84567,"position":16,"arabic":"خَفِيفًۭا","translation":"লঘু","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84568,"position":17,"arabic":"فَمَرَّتْ","translation":"অতঃপর সে চলাচল করে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84569,"position":18,"arabic":"بِهِۦ ۖ","translation":"নিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84571,"position":19,"arabic":"فَلَمَّآ","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84572,"position":20,"arabic":"أَثْقَلَت","translation":"ভারী হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84573,"position":21,"arabic":"دَّعَوَا","translation":"দু'জনেই দোয়া করে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84574,"position":22,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহর (কাছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84575,"position":23,"arabic":"رَبَّهُمَا","translation":"(যিনি) তাদের উভয়ের রব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84576,"position":24,"arabic":"لَئِنْ","translation":"\"অবশ্যই যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84577,"position":25,"arabic":"ءَاتَيْتَنَا","translation":"দাও তুমি আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84578,"position":26,"arabic":"صَـٰلِحًۭا","translation":"পূর্ণাঙ্গ ও সন্তান","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84579,"position":27,"arabic":"لَّنَكُونَنَّ","translation":"আবশ্যই আমরা হবো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84580,"position":28,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84581,"position":29,"arabic":"ٱلشَّـٰكِرِينَ","translation":"কৃতজ্ঞদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_189_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84582,"position":30,"arabic":"١٨٩","translation":"(১৮৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":190,"arabic":"فَلَمَّآ ءَاتَىٰهُمَا صَٰلِحًۭا جَعَلَا لَهُۥ شُرَكَآءَ فِيمَآ ءَاتَىٰهُمَا ۚ فَتَعَٰلَى ٱللَّهُ عَمَّا يُشْرِكُونَ","translation":"And yet, as soon as He has granted them sound [offspring], they begin to ascribe to other powers beside Him a share in bringing about what He has granted them! Sublimely exalted, however, is God- above anything to which men may ascribe a share in His divinity!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1144.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":84595,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّآ","translation":"অত:পর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_190_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84596,"position":2,"arabic":"ءَاتَىٰهُمَا","translation":"দু’জনকে দিলেন তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_190_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{